			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Did this today with the following:
<br />
Warrior
<br />
Paladin
<br />
Rogue
<br />
Mage (me)
<br />
Cleric x 2
<br />
Cleric, (my sucky bot cleric)
<br />
Bard
<br />

<br />
All Tacvi+ geared (sans my bot cleric)
<br />
Looong fight.  The real key seems to be DPS and bard resists.  The AEs are brutal, but with a bard they became quite tolerable.  Also, just keeping a level head and healing smart.  Setup a mini CH chain if you have to, but use mana sparingly and use things like celestial regen / divine arb.
<br />

<br />
Best tactics so far--
<br />
clear east part of room with gnome
<br />
move raid down to air pocket in lava
<br />
mage goes up and does turnin
<br />
gnome spawns elemental which moves to middle of pocket of air where MT is waiting.
<br />
fire essence is roote and rampages occasionally (really small range).
<br />
nukes hardly landed, so melee dps + lures are best<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=653282" target=_blank>Casala</a>
<br />
<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1023548" target=_blank>Aderyn- cleric bot</a>
<br />
<a href="http://www.hneguild.com" target=_blank>Heaven and Earth</a>
<br />
Saryrn</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
