				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">How i got my fire part: My SK buddy escorted me to the lava  air-bubble (had to kill 1 mob on the way) then I coh'd 24 early-EP geared people right to the spot.  
<br />

<br />
Buffed up raid and I invised out to the halfling, did the hand-in and said "ready", and swam back to raid. You dont need to kill any ogre in the forge room.  Fire Essence comes to raid, and goes down after a 4 min fight  - maybe it was faster, but it seemed like an eternity to me :-)
<br />

<br />
We had  to rez about 8 people, 11k tank survived witout big problems (5 clerics in raid, no cycle, just spam from time to time). Oh, and I drowned, hehe.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=662246" target="_blank" class="postlink">Kaggers</a> on bertoxx</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
